Questions:check whether a character is vowel or consonant
step1:understand the problem
what is given? it is character=a 
what is the output? vowel
what is required? condition
step2:manual check
a-->aeiou-->vowel
c-->aeiou-->consonant
step3:write a logic in plain english
  1.give a variable name vowel and store aeiou value
  2.it check if the input in vowel
    print "vowel"
  3.otherwise, print"consonant"
step4:write a code
    def vowel(ch):
       vowels='aeiou'
       if ch in vowels:
         print("vowels")
       else:
         print("consonants")
